title: Ministry of Sound the Annual 2015 (Mixed

Kronic is one of AustraliaÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s production prodigies, operating as a reckless party starter with an alarming disregard for personal safety, all whilst killing the 2014 Beatport charts next to heavy competition. The Annual 2015 sees Ministry of Sound Australia popping the champagne on delivering 200 compilations of the best dance music from Australia and overseas.
